[node name="HelpLabel" type="Label" parent="HelpPanel"]
layout_mode = 2
text = "Keyboard Shortcuts

Map Navigation:
  Middle-drag / Alt+drag: Pan
  Scroll / Pinch: Zoom

Tools (click or use buttons):
  Paint / Fill / Erase / Edge / POI / Region / Select
  E / Shift+E: Elevation +/-
  [ / ]: Brush size
  0-9: Select terrain

Selection & Stamps:
  Select tool: Click or drag-box (Shift adds)
  Cmd/Ctrl+C: Copy selection
  Cmd/Ctrl+Shift+V: Paste stamp
  Cmd/Ctrl+X: Cut selection
  R / Shift+R: Rotate stamp
  M: Mirror stamp

File Operations:
  Cmd/Ctrl+S: Save
  Cmd/Ctrl+O: Open
  Cmd/Ctrl+V: Validate map

Press any key to close..."

